Release Notes:

The Handsome Family's eighth studio album, "Honey Moon," takes
place under bowed branches & deep within winding corn mazes.
The release celebrates the duo's twentieth year of marriage
with a series of love songs that sharply contrast the dark
themes of their previous seven albums. "Honey Moon," is a
headphone record with layer upon layer of cool, weird
treasures waiting to be discovered with successive listens.
